    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor? I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, it is in pristine condition! It\u2019s been pampered, garage-kept, and honestly still has that fresh car feel. No scratches, no dents\u2014just pure perfection. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it because I love it, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this flawless beauty. Swing by and take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
