      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW\u2019s engineering prowess, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The chassis remains taut and responsive, benefiting from a reinforced rear subframe and a limited-slip differential that ensures optimal torque distribution. Mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, the powertrain delivers linear acceleration and a visceral mechanical soundtrack. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained, with documented rod bearing replacement and no signs of subframe fatigue. The exterior finish and interior upholstery are in showroom-ready state, reflecting a lifetime of climate-controlled storage and obsessive preventative maintenance.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
